{"tid":603416,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[哈利波特] 英文wordplay vs中文","createTime":"2018-03-23T17:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T06:35:19.000Z","uid":90749,"like":57,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"988e16815ff357e4b594ecfaca1961ad790f635e","tid":603416,"uid":90749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T17:23:32.000Z","msg":"見到有個PO有人講起Harry Potter D 翻譯 (飛鼠VS飛七)<br />\n咁話說小弟好鐘意睇HP, 英文版小說睇咗起碼3次, 中文版都睇過3次.<br />\n覺得JK 原著英文有好多原文玩word play 玩到好出神入化<br />\n但被翻譯成中文之後都失去咗個味道<br />\n<br />\n例如:<br />\n<br />\nMirror of Erised 意若思鏡<br />\nErised = Desire (掉轉隻字黎串, 象徵鏡入面反射既影像)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTom Marvolo Riddle = I am Lord Voldemort <br />\n(呢個玩anagram 重組字母, 湯姆 魔佛羅 瑞斗 = 我係佛地魔王)<br />\n<br />\nHogwarts 霍格華茲 (雙關語)= Hog (野豬) + warts (疣)<br />\n<br />\n創校4人: <br />\nGodric Gryffindor<br />\nSalazar Slytherin<br />\nRowena Ravencalw<br />\nHelga Hufflepuff <br />\n仲有: Severus Snape, Peter Pettigrew, Parvati Patil, Minerva McGonagall, etc... <br />\n全部玩 Alliteration (頭韻)<br />\n<br />\nQuadditch 魁地奇入面既波有快浮x1 +  搏格 x2 + 金探子x1:<br />\n<strong>Qua</strong>ffle + Blu<strong>d</strong>ger + Sn<strong>itch</strong> = <strong>Quadditch</strong><br />\n<br />\nOWLs (Ordinary Wizarding Levels)  (縮寫雙關: 貓頭鷹) 直譯咗做 普等巫測<br />\nNEWTs (蠑螈)<br />\n (Nastily Exhausting Wizarding Tests) 超級疲勞轟炸巫術測驗 <br />\n<br />\nKnight Bus (騎士公車 , 台灣譯名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) = Night bus同音雙關<br />\nGrimmauld Place 古里某街 = Grim old place 同音, 陰暗殘舊既地方  <br />\nFloo Network (呼嚕網) = Flue network 同音 (flue = 煙囪)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae081749489e9c943ea30d273fb0b5db08a5e844","tid":603416,"uid":164738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T17:42:32.000Z","msg":"我次次睇